{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And most of the experiences that went through during the war, we did together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he, in fact, remembered far more about all the things than I did.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I've learned a lot from him, really, in reminding me of all the things that we did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So going back to Berlin, then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We remember going, for example, to the zoo.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We, we happen to have loads of photographs from those olden days in Berlin, which survived the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because during the war, we gave all our documentation to friends who kept them for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got them back after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we have loads of photographs from those early days in Berlin with Ruti and me in the zoo, and in the back garden, and entertaining various visitors who came to see us, especially uncle and aunt, brother and sister of my father-- Uncle Rudi, Aunt [?",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Liesl. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of the things that my father liked in particular was he was an early trainspotter.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to go to one of the main stations in Berlin called the Anhalter Bahnhof.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a special treat for us at the weekend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to walk there and see all the big trains that went all over Europe in those days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, say, the zoo was another feature that we often went to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Feeding the animals, maybe, and then things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, it's, it's all those photographs that we have from those days really that remind us of that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to many other parts of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were-- there were lakes and all sorts of sites to see.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We also remember that we had very nice holidays in those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went to, to holiday, for example, to Marienbad in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
